{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this short but intense action-adventure game, you play as a faceless guardian, the last protector of a dying village lost in the endless desert. When a lone traveler destroys the village\u2019s only water source, you are tasked with delivering justice\u2014only to uncover a deeper mystery that could halt the relentless desertification of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With  responsive combat, easy-to-learn mechanics, and about two hours of fast-paced action, Faceless is an accessible yet challenging experience. Master its fluid movement and strategic encounters to uncover the truth and reclaim the desert\u2019s lost life. The fate of your village\u2014and perhaps the world\u2014rests in the hands of a warrior with no face, but endless resolve.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3506840?t=1739817073","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3506840?t=1739817073","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3506840/af533d868d08e4a333cfc30e7423fef7d9036e80/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739817073","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3506840/af533d868d08e4a333cfc30e7423fef7d9036e80/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739817073","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this short but intense action-adventure game, you play as a faceless guardian, the last protector of a dying village lost in the endless desert. When a lone traveler destroys the village\u2019s only water source, you are tasked with delivering justice\u2014only to uncover a deeper mystery that could halt the relentles